OL,3,CHealth board criticised after patient,
OL,4,C70, dies in 'unnecessary pain'
OL,6,FKay Picton, 70, from Tylorstown in
OL,7,FRhondda Cynon Taf, died of multi-organ
OL,8,Ffailure after contracting sepsis
OL,9,Ffollowing a diagnosis of bile duct
OL,10,Fcancer.
OL,12,FOn 13 June 2022, she attended the
OL,13,FRoyal Glamorgan Hospital with symptoms
OL,14,Fof vomiting, being unable to eat and
OL,15,Fdrink, weight loss and feeling weak.
OL,16,FShe died in their care 16 days later.
