OL,3,CHealth board criticised after patient,
OL,4,C70, dies in 'unnecessary pain'
OL,6,FThe investigation was launched after
OL,7,FKay's daughter, Dawn Williams,
OL,8,Fcomplained about the care and
OL,9,Ftreatment her late mother received
OL,10,Ffrom Cwm Taf Morgannwg Health Board.
OL,12,FThe Ombudsman's final report into the
OL,13,Fcomplaint found failings in obtaining
OL,14,Fconsent from Mrs Picton, and in
OL,15,Frelation to appropriate post-operative
OL,16,Fcare including monitoring, pain relief
OL,17,Fand oral care.
