OL,3,CHealth board criticised after patient,
OL,4,C70, dies in 'unnecessary pain'
OL,6,FThe Ombudsman said she was left with
OL,7,F"no option" to issue a public interest
OL,8,Freport after the Health Board ignored
OL,9,Frequests from her staff to comment on
OL,10,Fthe draft report.
OL,12,FThis is not an "isolated issue",
OL,13,Faccording to Michelle Morris, but is
OL,14,Fan example of several cases where the
OL,15,FCwm Taf Morgannwg Health Board has
OL,16,Ffailed to provide information or
OL,17,Fcomments.
