OL,3,CHealth board criticised after patient,
OL,4,C70, dies in 'unnecessary pain'
OL,6,FThe Ombudsman says she has been in
OL,7,Fcontact with the Health Board about
OL,8,Fthese delays and met with the Chief
OL,9,FExecutive.
OL,11,FCommenting on the report Ms Morris,
OL,12,Fsaid: "I am deeply concerned about the
OL,13,Finaction of the Health Board.
OL,15,F"The Health Board was given a number
OL,16,Fof opportunities to comment on a draft
OL,17,Fof this report, but it has not done so.
